Optional subtitle appears below on some pages (Projects, Sources):
```tsx
<p
  className="mt-1 text-[13px] text-[#6b7280]"
  style={{ fontFamily: "var(--font-dm-sans)" }}
>
  Tracked software projects and their recent releases.
