```

Used in: Releases, Channels, Subscriptions pages

**Table header row:**
```tsx
<tr style={{ backgroundColor: "#fafaf9" }}>
  {["Name", "Type", "Config"].map((heading) => (
    <th
      className="px-4 py-3 text-left"
