  </Button>
</Link>
```

---

### 9. **Color Palette Reference**

| Purpose | Color | Usage |
|---------|-------|-------|
| Primary text | `#111113` | Headings, main content |
| Secondary text | `#6b7280` | Dates, descriptions |
| Muted text | `#9ca3af` | Labels, hints, disabled |
| Light muted | `#c4c4c0` | Very subtle text |
| Borders | `#e8e8e5` | Card borders, dividers |
| Backgrounds | `#fafaf9` | Hover states, header bg |
| White | `#ffffff` | Card background |
| Accent | `#e8601a` | Primary buttons/links |
| Monospace text | `#374151` | Code/versions |

---

### 10. **Responsive List Item Cards (Projects Page)**

```tsx
function ProjectCard({ project }: { project: Project }) {
  return (
    <div
      className="overflow-hidden rounded-md"
      style={{ border: "1px solid #e8e8e5", backgroundColor: "#ffffff" }}
    >
      {/* Header */}
      <div className="px-4 py-3">
        <Link
          href={`/projects/${project.id}`}
          className="group inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[16px] font-bold transition-colors"
          style={{ fontFamily: "var(--font-fraunces)", color: "#e8601a" }}
        >
          {project.name}
          <ArrowRight className="h-3.5 w-3.5 opacity-0 -translate-x-1 transition-all group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0" />
        </Link>
        {project.description && (
          <p
            className="mt-0.5 text-[13px] truncate"
            style={{ color: "#6b7280", fontFamily: "var(--font-dm-sans)" }}
          >
            {project.description}
          </p>
        )}
      </div>

      {/* Content columns: sources | recent releases | semantic releases */}
      <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 border-t" style={{ borderColor: "#e8e8e5" }}>
        {/* Sections */}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

---

## Summary of Key Takeaways

1. **Typography:** Fraunces for headings, DM Sans for body/labels, JetBrains Mono for technical content
2. **Spacing:** Tables use `px-4 py-3` for cells, cards use `px-4 py-3` for content
3. **Borders:** Subtle `#e8e8e5` lines, `rounded-lg` or `rounded-md` for corners
4. **Hover states:** `hover:bg-[#fafaf9]` for rows/items, subtle color transitions
5. **Action buttons:** Orange accent `#e8601a` with white text, icon buttons use gray with hover darkening
6. **Badges:** Use semantic colors (red for critical, orange for high), pill-shaped with icons
7. **Empty states:** Centered Fraunces italic text at `15px`, full-width containers with borders
8. **Loading:** Simple gray text, `py-16` vertical padding

All files are located in `/Users/pc/web3/ReleaseBeacon/web/` with key patterns in:
- Page files: `web/app/*/page.tsx`
- Components: `web/components/ui/version-chip.tsx`, `provider-badge.tsx`

