| Borders | `#e8e8e5` | Card borders, dividers |
| Backgrounds | `#fafaf9` | Hover states, header bg |
| White | `#ffffff` | Card background |
| Accent | `#e8601a` | Primary buttons/links |
| Monospace text | `#374151` | Code/versions |

